# Do Not Edit Outreach Template Without Explicit User Request

- Treat `.local/ai-outreach/email-template.md` as protected.
- Do not create, modify, or reformat this file unless the user explicitly asks to change this exact file in the current request.
- If a task would normally involve updating templates, skip this file and proceed with other required changes.
- If uncertain, ask before touching it.

